trans-unit.source: Represents a query that tests whether a message satisfies both specified <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en spørring som tester om en melding oppfyller begge angitt <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Matches performed by this filter will always evaluate both <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter> objects before returning a result.
trans-unit.target: Treff utført av filteret alltid evaluerer begge <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter>objekter før den returnerer et resultat.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter>

trans-unit.source: This AND operation does not short circuit if the first <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter> evaluated returns false.
trans-unit.target: Operasjonen og støtter ikke kort krets Hvis først <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter>evaluerte returneres false.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.StrictAndMessageFilter"></xref> class using the specified <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.StrictAndMessageFilter"> </xref> klasse parametersettet med de angitte <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: Tests whether a message matches both of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"></xref> objects specified in this filter.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer om en melding som samsvarer med både den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"> </xref> objekter som angis i dette filteret.

trans-unit.source: **true** if the message contained in the buffer matches both message filters; otherwise, **false**.
trans-unit.target: **TRUE** Hvis meldingen i bufferen samsvarer med begge meldingen filtrene; ellers **false**.

trans-unit.source: Tests whether a buffered message matches both of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"></xref> objects specified in this filter.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer om en bufret melding samsvarer med både den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter"> </xref> objekter som angis i dette filteret.

trans-unit.source: When testing for a match condition, both <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter> objects are evaluated before returning a result.
trans-unit.target: Når du tester for en samsvarer betingelse begge <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter>objekter evalueres før den returnerer et resultat.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.MessageFilter>

trans-unit.source: **true** if the message contained in the buffer matches both message filters; otherwise, **false**.
trans-unit.target: **TRUE** Hvis meldingen i bufferen samsvarer med begge meldingen filtrene; ellers **false**.
